{
  "stem": "3040.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was in October, but there was a blizzard in Greenland.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had to dis-- de-embark-- de-embark?-- the plane, and go over to some, you know, to-- like on the airport.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because either they changed place or whatever, they couldn't keep us in the place for hours.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I remember carrying the baby, walking through that deep snow, from the plane.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because they were-- the facilities were not like they have it now, the modern facilities, you go directly from the-- from the plane to the-- to the-- not to the airport, to the-- to the facilities there.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we were walking through the snow, heavy snow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we waited there, until they announced that the next plane is ready.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they took us, brought us here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The whole voyage, the whole trip, took us 30 hours.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Arriving here at the airport, they took us to Ellis Island from the airport.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "At Ellis Island, I was met by my aunt, who survived this uncle who sent me the affidavit, and my cousins, which is his-- her-- her sons-- son.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my sister was here already before.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She-- she came three months earlier than I did.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They're waiting, and my brother also came before me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they were all waiting for me at Ellis Island-- for us, actually.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we brought us to-- to the apartment where my aunt lived, in the Bronx.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was a widow.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And actually, she wanted to go to Israel after the death of her husband, my uncle.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But she decided since he sent us affidavits, she decided to stay and to keep the apartment for us, that we can have it when we come.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So it was a very noble deed of-- on her part.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so we came to her apartment.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
